725588f-a.title: Queens: 69th Street - 66th Road
725588f-a.text:
89th Street, west side, between 66th Road and 66th Drive,
showing Wagenbrenner's masonry yard. An old farmhouse is in
back of the garage.
P. L. Sperr  July 2, 1935
NO REPRODUCTIONS

725587f-a.title: Queens: 69th Street - 66th Drive
725587f-a.text:
69th Street, east side, at 65th Drive, showing the Trinity
Lutheran Church. The sign over the basement doorway reads:
Charles T. Schmmedcke--Glass specialties.
P. L. Sperr  July 2, 1935
NO REPRODUCTIONS
